	</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">good job\nKeep up the power</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Use WordPress &amp; WooCommerce to Sell Online</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/houdyk\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5f5370ce8f59f934778c423569f29246?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5f5370ce8f59f934778c423569f29246?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/houdyk\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Jeroen Houdijk <small>(houdyk)</small></a> el <span class=\"review-date\">marzo 9, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><strong>Use WordPress &amp; WooCommerce to Sell Online</strong>\n\nWhen I tried to create my first e-commerce in 2011 I failed with Magento and and other complicated platforms.\n\nThe combination of WordPress with WooCommerce is by far the most powerful online e-commerce platform if you want to keep things simple and effective.\n\nI know you build beautiful web-shops with it. I use it for one product stores or for people who want to sell just a few products as extra revenue stream for their website.\n\nAdding a simple digital product to your self hosted website is by far 